maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 3 Evening” game were:
6-5-5, Wild: 8
(six, five, five; Wild: eight)
